extends ../new/layout_tailwind
block css
block js
block content
    div(class="max-w-7xl mx-auto p-4")
        div(class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg mb-8")
            h2(class="text-center text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#332D56] bg-gray-200 py-4 rounded-t-lg")
                | Shipping Policy
            div(class="p-6")
                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 1. Introduction
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | At Agricultural Produce Market Committee, APMC Amalner, we
                        |  ensure the timely and efficient processing of agricultural produce.
                        |  Below is the detailed overview of our services and policies to
                        |  maintain transparency and customer satisfaction.

                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 2. Produce Handling
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | Our committee manages the buying, selling, and storage of
                        |  agricultural produce with the highest standards of safety and
                        |  quality. We strive to ensure minimal delays and optimal market
                        |  conditions for our traders and farmers.

                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 3. Availability of Facilities
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | The market facilities are open 6 days a week, providing flexibility
                        |  to buyers and sellers. Our goal is to offer a smooth experience with
                        |  no disruptions in the service throughout the year.

                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 4. Product Registration
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | Farmers and traders can register their products for sale with ease.
                        |  Once registered, they can participate in market events and
                        |  transactions at our designated market yard.

                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 5. Customer Support
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | Our dedicated customer service team is available to assist you with
                        |  any queries or issues related to registration, product handling, or
                        |  market operations. Please contact us for any assistance you may
                        |  require.

                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 6. Regular Updates
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | We regularly update our practices and services to align with the
                        |  best market standards and government regulations. Stay informed with
                        |  timely updates on our operations, policies, and new offerings.

                p(class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4")
                    | Thank you for choosing Agricultural Produce Market Committee, APMC Amalner,
                    |  for your agricultural needs. If you have any questions or
                    |  need further assistance, feel free to reach out to our customer support
                    |  team. We look forward to supporting your agricultural endeavors.
